M|CTA |Appr|
M|CTA |tx|**nz**
M|CTA |it|"Shop the drop →"
M|CTA |it|"Explore the collection"
M|CTA |it|"Read the edit"
M|CTA |it|"See how it's worn"
M|CTA |tx|**hb**
M|CTA |it|"Start for free"
M|CTA |it|"See how it works"
M|CTA |it|"Try it in 2 minutes"
M|CTA |it|"Your money, simplified"
